    note right of TilingDefaultCompressionDefault
        T = Tiling dimension: Default=NotExplicit, ExplicitNoParams, ExplicitWithParams
        C = Compression dimension: Default=NotExplicit, ExplicitNoType, ExplicitWithType
        Initial state: both tiling and compression in non-EXPLICIT mode (MODE_COPY_FROM_METADATA default)
    end note

    note right of TilingDefaultCompressionExplicitNoType
        Compression is MODE_EXPLICIT but no type set yet.
        setCompressionType, getCompressionType, unsetCompression available.
        setCompressionQuality/getCompressionQuality/getBitRate still throw IllegalStateException.
    end note

    note right of TilingDefaultCompressionExplicitWithType
        Compression is MODE_EXPLICIT and type is set.
        All compression methods available.
    end note

    note right of TilingExplicitWithParamsCompressionDefault
        Tiling is MODE_EXPLICIT and setTiling() has been called.
        getTileWidth/Height/GridX/GridY available.
    end note
